{
  "video_id": "YvA1O7MYs_w",
  "title": "Scripts as Behaviour Components - Unity Official Tutorials",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 442.0,
      "end_time": 2769.0,
      "text": "Scripts should be considered as behaviour"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2769.0,
      "end_time": 4409.0,
      "text": "components in Unity."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4633.0,
      "end_time": 6633.0,
      "text": "As with other components in Unity they can"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6633.0,
      "end_time": 8288.0,
      "text": "be applied to objects and are seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8288.0,
      "end_time": 9538.0,
      "text": "in the inspector."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10380.0,
      "end_time": 12442.0,
      "text": "With this particular example, this cube"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12442.0,
      "end_time": 15245.0,
      "text": "has a rigidbody component which gives it"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15245.0,
      "end_time": 18157.0,
      "text": "a physical mass. And when you press play"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18158.0,
      "end_time": 19697.0,
      "text": "the cube falls to the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19697.0,
      "end_time": 21697.0,
      "text": "as it uses gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22197.0,
      "end_time": 25540.0,
      "text": "We also have added an examples script."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25872.0,
      "end_time": 28284.0,
      "text": "This behaviour script has code in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28284.0,
      "end_time": 30284.0,
      "text": "which changes the colour of the cube"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30284.0,
      "end_time": 32702.0,
      "text": "by effecting the colour value of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32703.000000000004,
      "end_time": 35397.0,
      "text": "default material attached to that object."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36228.0,
      "end_time": 38925.0,
      "text": "When we press the R key on the keyboard"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39425.0,
      "end_time": 41187.0,
      "text": "the colour gets changed to red."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 41411.0,
      "end_time": 43360.0,
      "text": "When we press G the colour gets"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43360.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "changed to green. And when we press B"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 47460.0,
      "text": "it gets changed to blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47877.0,
      "end_time": 49877.0,
      "text": "By attaching this script to the object"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 49877.0,
      "end_time": 51877.0,
      "text": "when we refer to game object"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 51877.0,
      "end_time": 54185.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re referring to this particular item."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 54630.0,
      "end_time": 56630.0,
      "text": "We then drill down to the value that we want"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 56630.0,
      "end_time": 59597.0,
      "text": "and effect it. Here we&#39;re addressing the"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 59597.0,
      "end_time": 61597.0,
      "text": "game object this script is attached to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 61597.0,
      "end_time": 63597.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re then addressing the renderer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 64959.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66969.99999999999,
      "text": "which is the component seen here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 66970.0,
      "end_time": 68567.0,
      "text": "mesh renderer. We&#39;re then addressing the"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 68567.0,
      "end_time": 70678.0,
      "text": "material attached to that renderer and"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 70678.0,
      "end_time": 72958.0,
      "text": "finally the colour of that material."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 73209.0,
      "end_time": 76212.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re setting it to a shortcut called red"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 76532.0,
      "end_time": 78351.0,
      "text": "which is part of the colour class."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78351.0,
      "end_time": 79992.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see this in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 80422.0,
      "end_time": 83437.0,
      "text": "If I press play, then use the R, G or B"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 83437.0,
      "end_time": 86233.0,
      "text": "keys on the keyboard I can change the colour."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 86567.0,
      "end_time": 88244.0,
      "text": "And you can see that the material"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 88245.0,
      "end_time": 89662.0,
      "text": "is being effected."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 90162.0,
      "end_time": 92945.0,
      "text": "So this material is applied to the renderer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 93335.0,
      "end_time": 95625.0,
      "text": "default diffuse, you can see that listed there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 96125.0,
      "end_time": 98848.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re then effecting the main colour value"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 98848.0,
      "end_time": 100848.0,
      "text": "and setting it to a certain value in here."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 101860.0,
      "end_time": 103860.0,
      "text": "The same as it would if I was actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 103860.0,
      "end_time": 105860.0,
      "text": "doing it by hand in the editor."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 105724.0,
      "end_time": 108343.0,
      "text": "Scripts can be created in the project panel"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 108343.0,
      "end_time": 110343.0,
      "text": "by choosing Create and then choosing"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110343.0,
      "end_time": 112343.0,
      "text": "a language of your choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112843.0,
      "end_time": 113937.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 117309.0,
      "end_time": 119309.0,
      "text": "they can then be attached to objects either"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 119309.0,
      "end_time": 120973.0,
      "text": "by dragging and dropping"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 123766.0,
      "end_time": 126765.0,
      "text": "or by choosing the Add Component button"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 126765.0,
      "end_time": 128764.0,
      "text": "at the bottom of the Component menu"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 128764.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130764.00000000001,
      "text": "and then choosing from the list of scripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 130764.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132422.0,
      "text": "in your current project."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 133600.0,
      "end_time": 135600.0,
      "text": "Scripts can also be created using the"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 135600.0,
      "end_time": 136862.0,
      "text": "Add Component button by choosing"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136862.0,
      "end_time": 138862.0,
      "text": "New Script from the bottom and naming"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138862.0,
      "end_time": 141351.0,
      "text": "the script and selecting a language type"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 141351.0,
      "end_time": 142518.0,
      "text": "from the drop-down menu."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 142963.0,
      "end_time": 146674.0,
      "text": "This can then be created and added in one step."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151664.0,
      "end_time": 153664.0,
      "text": "The final way to add a script to your"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 153664.0,
      "end_time": 156594.0,
      "text": "object is to select the object in the hierarchy"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156594.0,
      "end_time": 159385.0,
      "text": "and then choose Components - Scripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159385.0,
      "end_time": 161274.0,
      "text": "and then choose from the list of scripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161274.0,
      "end_time": 163274.0,
      "text": "in your current project. Of course you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 163274.0,
      "end_time": 165190.0,
      "text": "apply scripts to do all manner of other"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 165190.0,
      "end_time": 167413.0,
      "text": "behaviours of objects. Try to think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 167413.0,
      "end_time": 169413.0,
      "text": "scripts as components that you create"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 169413.0,
      "end_time": 171413.0,
      "text": "yourself, allowing you to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 171413.0,
      "end_time": 173413.0,
      "text": "behaviour for different game objects in"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173413.0,
      "end_time": 175413.0,
      "text": "your game, this could be characters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175413.0,
      "end_time": 177413.0,
      "text": "it could be environments or it could be"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177413.0,
      "end_time": 179148.0,
      "text": "scripts that manage the functionality"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 179148.0,
      "end_time": 179846.0,
      "text": "of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 180346.0,
      "end_time": 182346.0,
      "text": "This example script that we&#39;ve looked at"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 182346.0,
      "end_time": 184553.0,
      "text": "is written in C# but in Unity"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184553.0,
      "end_time": 188582.0,
      "text": "you can write in Javascript, C# and Boo."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 188972.0,
      "end_time": 191970.0,
      "text": "Boo is a derivative of Python, though"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 191970.0,
      "end_time": 193415.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not as commonly used as the other two."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 193653.0,
      "end_time": 196149.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;ll likely see Javascript or C#"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 196149.0,
      "end_time": 198149.0,
      "text": "examples when you see scripting"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 198149.0,
      "end_time": 200149.0,
      "text": "from Unity around the web. The videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 200149.0,
      "end_time": 202149.0,
      "text": "that you see in this learning area"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 202149.0,
      "end_time": 204149.0,
      "text": "will be written in C# but we&#39;ll also"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 204149.0,
      "end_time": 206252.0,
      "text": "provide the Javascript equivalent"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 206252.0,
      "end_time": 207642.0,
      "text": "beneath the video."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 207642.0,
      "end_time": 208000.0,
      "text": "Subtitles by the Amara.org community"
    }
  ]
